    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This specimen excels mechanically, with the individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous transient response and a linear power delivery up to the 8,400 RPM redline. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the replacement of rod bearings with treated shells and upgraded throttle actuators. The chassis retains its composure via Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution during corner exit. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the subframe and suspension bushings remain within factory tolerances, preserving the communicative hydraulic steering feel. A mechanically honest example for the purist who prioritizes powertrain integrity and chassis dynamics.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
