    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood\u2014typical for its mileage but otherwise striking. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no tears, and the dashboard remains free of cracks or sun damage. Every electronic feature, from the responsive touchscreen navigation to the heated seats and dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is solid. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, recently receiving a fresh oil change and a new set of all-season tires. The engine runs smoothly without any odd noises, and the transmission shifts seamlessly. It\u2019s a reliable, comfortable, and well-cared-for machine ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
